'''Alpha Nonce''' was a [[Space station/Legends|port station]] in the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]] some 55 [[Standard year/Legends|years]] before the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|Battle of Geonosis]]. [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Galim Eddawan]] was once scheduled to arrive there, but he never did.

